# Rails models

Read `docs/standards/stacks/rails8/technical-guideline.md` §3 for full detail.

- Balanced ActiveRecord: associations, validations, scopes, lightweight entity logic
- No multi-step orchestration or external provider calls
- No `default_scope` — use named scopes
